Organizers stated that 2.5 million people attended, and police stated that there were 1.9 million &mdash; figures which would make the event the largest of its kind in the world &mdash; including 700,000 visitors from other cities and countries.  This was an increase from 2004, when police stated that 1.5 million people attended.  

